title: Tessanne Chin In Between Words
description: Growing up on the island of Jamaica with musical parents, Tessanne knew she always wanted to be a musician. For three years, she sang backup for reggae legend Jimmy Cliff, but eventually broke out as a solo artist in Jamaica. Tessanne has not been able to make any waves in the U.S., but she's hoping that The Voice will take her global. Follow Tessanne on Twitter at @Tessanne
